 -Robert Koester

content: This is a fantastic companion to the book and a must have for search managers in the field. Well worth the money.
Comprehensive app with detailed information. Worth every cent.
It is very helpful to be able to quickly reference key information from the Lost Person Behavior book when running a SAR mission.  Thanks for the app!
Gives everything from what to do when first on scene at a specific incident all the way down to what resources to send when and where. The most comprehensive set of data available for SAR.
Handy format for invaluable information!

The book has been  invaluable as a SAR resource.   This app puts that knowledge right on your belt so when you get the call from LE  of "what do we do next?"  the answer is right at your fingertips.  Highly recommend it for every SAR person and organization.  Take the class in order to understand the theory behind the charts and how to apply them.

The LPB book has been an invaluable resource for the Search and Rescue community.  To have this information more readily available and to more persons will change the way responders on my team manage the critical onset of the mission.
